title: Tegna, Dish spar over contract fees - The Wichita Eagle
text:
TV station operator Tegna Inc. has cut off Dish Network subscribers' access to its local channels in more than three dozen markets because of a contract dispute between the two sides. At issue is that satellite broadcaster Dish refuses to pay the rate increase pushed by Tegna for retransmission consent fees.
 The Wichita Eagle.
